title: Pending
description: A bid has been submitted but not yet evaluated.

title: Valid
description: The submitted bid met the qualification requirements in order to be evaluated.

title: Disqualified
description: The submitted bid did not meet the qualification requirements in order to be evaluated.

title: Withdrawn
description: The submitted bid was withdrawn by the tenderer(s).

title: Winning
description: The bid was selected as a winning one
